{"title":"阿里轻量云服务器ssl证书部署","date":"2018-09-18T15:19:40.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Sep 18, 2018","L":"09/18/2018","MM-DD":"09-18"},"link":"Learning/d97b541a2c03","tags":["SSL","免费SSL证书"],"categories":["Learning"],"updated":"2023-11-14T12:07:06.466Z","content":"<p><img src=\"http://blog.wujun.sc.cn/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ssl_%E7%9C%8B%E5%9B%BE%E7%8E%8B.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"φbs\"></p>\n<p>在阿里购买了一个免费的一年ssl证书，下载下来后按照阿里给的教程没有安装成功，之后自己在网上找的一个方法，这里做个记录一下。</p>\n<h2 id=\"第一步，上传证书文件到服务器\">第一步，上传证书文件到服务器<a title=\"#第一步，上传证书文件到服务器\" href=\"#第一步，上传证书文件到服务器\"></a></h2>\n<p>保存在/usr/local/apache/cert/目录下，cert目录是自己创建的，可以自己取其他名字。</p>\n<h2 id=\"第二步，配置http-vhosts.conf文件\">第二步，配置http-vhosts.conf文件<a title=\"#第二步，配置http-vhosts.conf文件\" href=\"#第二步，配置http-vhosts.conf文件\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ServerAdmin webmaster@serveradmin.com </span><br><span class=\"line\">DocumentRoot <span class=\"string\">&quot;/home/www/htdocs/dc&quot;</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\">ServerName 你的域名 </span><br><span class=\"line\">SSLEngine on </span><br><span class=\"line\">SSLProtocol all -SSLv2 -SSLv3 </span><br><span class=\"line\">SSLCipherSuite HIGH:!RC4:!MD5:!aNULL:!eNULL:!NULL:!DH:!EDH:!EXP:+MEDIUM </span><br><span class=\"line\">SSLCertificateFile cert/public.pem <span class=\"comment\">#三个证书文件 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">SSLCertificateKeyFile cert/214*********453.key <span class=\"comment\">#三个证书文件 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">SSLCertificateChainFile cert/chain.pem <span class=\"comment\">#三个证书文件 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ProxyPassMatch ^/(.*\\.php(/.*)?)$ unix:/home/www/logs/php-fpm.sock|fcgi://127.0.0.1/home/www/htdocs/dc/  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>注：重点是端口一定要把原来的80改为443。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"第三步、重启\">第三步、重启<a title=\"#第三步、重启\" href=\"#第三步、重启\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apache /usr/local/apache/bin/apachectl restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"阿里云lnmp更换预装mysql遇到的坑","link":"Learning/fd412be05567"},"plink":"https://blog.jschef.com/Learning/d97b541a2c03/","toc":[{"id":"第一步，上传证书文件到服务器","title":"第一步，上传证书文件到服务器","index":"1"},{"id":"第二步，配置http-vhosts.conf文件","title":"第二步，配置http-vhosts.conf文件","index":"2"},{"id":"第三步、重启","title":"第三步、重启","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Chef Wu","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.jschef.com/Learning/d97b541a2c03/\" title=\"阿里轻量云服务器ssl证书部署\">https://blog.jschef.com/Learning/d97b541a2c03/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"September 18, 2018"}}